arts.ttl: Augsburg and Freiburg cancel each other out in goalless stalemate
arts.sum: Augsburg and Freiburg battled to a goalless draw in a match of missed opportunities and strong defensive displays, with Augsburg twice hitting the woodwork and Freiburg frustrated by record-breaking Finn Dahmen. The second half saw Freiburg come out with renewed vigour, but Finn Dahmen was equal to his first test of the day as he kept out Merlin Röhl's low drive to preserved his clean sheet.

arts.ttl: Freiburg’s stalemate in Augsburg deny a Bundesliga record
arts.sum: Augsburg are the only side to win a home point on matchday 24 after their goalless draw against Freiburg.
